description:
So what IS the real test for the final days? Many of us our missing the big picture. We must be very clear on what the true test for God’s people in the last days will be. The devil loves to throw up smokescreens and distractions to divert us from the real issues that affect our eternal life. We read of this test in that apocalyptic book of revelation. This video will help you to be prepared!
